<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8">
		<title></title>
		<style type="text/css">
			.list li:nth-child(2n){
				background: red;
			}
			.list li:nth-child(2n-1){
				background: blue;
			}
		</style>
		<script type="text/javascript">
			window.onload = function(){
				var v1 = document.getElementsByClassName("v1")[0];
				var v2 = document.getElementsByName("mytext")[0];
				var v3 = document.querySelector("#v3");
				var v4 = document.querySelectorAll("input")[3];
				var btn = document.getElementsByTagName("button")[0];
				btn.onclick = function(){
					alert("姓名："+v1.value+","+"年龄："+v2.value+",学历："+v3.value+",专业"+v4.value);
				}
				
				//2.
				var list = document.querySelector(".list");
				var oli = document.querySelectorAll("li");
				var i=0;
				setInterval(function(){
					i++;
					if(i%2==0){
						for(var j=0;j<oli.length;j++){
							if(j%2==0){
								oli[j].style.background = "blue";
							}else{
								oli[j].style.background = "red";
							}
						}
					}else{
						for(var j=0;j<oli.length;j++){
							if(j%2==0){
								oli[j].style.background = "red";
							}else{
								oli[j].style.background = "blue";
							}
						}
					}
				},1000)
				
				var oimg = document.querySelectorAll("img");
				for(var k=0;k<oimg.length-1;k++){
					oimg[k].onclick = function(){
						oimg[3].src = this.src;
					}
				}
			}
		</script>
	</head>
	<body>
		<h3>1、实现一个个人信息页面   姓名  年龄  学历  专业, 可以获取到输入的信息, 点击保存按钮以后, 弹出信息(信息显示形式: 姓名:张三,年龄:33,学历:本科,专业:计算机)</h3>
		<div class="box1">
			<input class="v1" type="text" placeholder="名字" />
			<input name="mytext" type="text" placeholder="年龄" />
			<input id="v3" type="text" placeholder="学历" />
			<input type="text" placeholder="专业" />
			<button>保存</button>
		</div>
		<h3>2、隔行变色（颜色1s切换一次，红变蓝，蓝变红）</h3>
		<ul class="list">
			<li>1</li>
			<li>2</li>
			<li>3</li>
			<li>4</li>
			<li>5</li>
			<li>6</li>
			<li>7</li>
			<li>8</li>
		</ul>
		<h3>3、点击前三张图片, 切换下面的图</h3>
		<img src="../../day08/上课代码/img/bird3.png" />
		<img src="../../day08/上课代码/img/bird4.png" />
		<img src="../../day08/上课代码/img/bird5.png" />
		<br />
		<img src="../../day08/上课代码/img/bird3.png" />
	</body>
</html>
